			<trans-unit id="module.about.extensionBody" resname="module.about.extensionBody">
				<source>This extension (id_be_login) adds a TYPO3 backend module to customize the administrator login screen: background image (local path, FAL folder, or remote service), logo and alt text, colors for the login card and sign-in button, footnote text, and login box placement, opacity, and corner radius. Settings are stored in the extension configuration and applied on the login page together with compatibility fallbacks to the core backend extension where values are left empty.</source>
			</trans-unit>
